channel.title: Deleting floors and roofs
channel.description:
Okay so i want to delete a bulding , i know how i delete the walls and stuff, but how do i delete the floor and the roof??
For roof just do upheight and then add the coord to deleteobject??
And how about the floor?? its not really a floor but im talking about the texture on the ground i want to change it into grass to costomize my home. I can edit the whole texture, but all of those places where this kind of texture is added will change too, and i only wanna remove 1 bulding.
Is this possible ?? Probably but does anyone know the answer?? i hope so. Please i need some help here guys.
